snippet.title: Worthless by Abliss
snippet.description:
Fret Smasher is a brand new band style rhythm game that will be available for PC later this year. More details about the game will be posted soon so be sure to subscribe to be the first to hear it!

Abliss' Facebook Page - https://www.facebook.com/ablissfans/

--

Join our Discord - https://discordapp.com/invite/F8vZW85

Follow our Twitter - https://twitter.com/FretSmasher

--

Programmed by:
AttarGuitar, DigiDuncan, FabeGabe, ItsNovaHere, and Roxra

Graphics by:
Michael
